{"tid":1045336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Tesla突然減價】強國車主憤怒！ 車行外抗議：二手車實跌價","createTime":"2019-03-03T13:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T15:35:29.000Z","uid":82845,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0693e8b94bf93d9ecaa5419661b98a54bd78c18","tid":1045336,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190303/large/1551595401_aa4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190303%2Flarge%2F1551595401_aa4f.jpg&h=52d7a0f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國電動車生產商特斯拉（Tesla）近日宣佈，全系列車款在華大幅減價，以提振中國市場的銷量。<span style=\"color: red;\">入門版Model 3減價2.6萬元人民幣（下同；3萬港元），現以40.7萬元（約47萬港元）出售，減價幅度最大的是Model X P100D，現售價84.82萬元（約99萬港元），比原價便宜34.11萬元</span>（約40萬港元）。不過，減價潮引起內地部份Tesla車主不滿，已有消費者組織維權，在車行外拉起橫額抗議：「特斯拉隨意降價，侵犯消費者合法權益！」<br />\n<br />\n電動車減價對準車主來說是好消息，但對於部份舊車主卻不是，認為廠家減價對他們是一種傷害，心理出現不平衡，二手車價勢必造成損失，要求Tesla賠償。因此，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有網民引伸出「許漲不許跌」、「只佔便宜絕不能吃虧」的話題，當初Tesla加價時，為甚麼這些車主不主動補償給車廠？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以Model X P100D為例，這一年多時間該車款價格一直處於浮動狀態，售價位於120萬至160萬元（約140萬至187萬港元）之間，當中涉及到官方調整或關稅問題，假如以當初160萬元的購車價來計算，如今售價下降至84.82萬元，一年多指導價就減了多達75萬元（約87萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\nTesla團隊宣佈，所有在減價前購買Tesla的車主，可以半價購買Autopilot自動輔助駕駛系統或全自動駕駛功能系統。從下月開始，舊車主只要花2,000美元（約1.5萬港元），即可升級擁有Autopilot自動輔助駕駛功能，或者額外再花3,000美元（約2.3萬港元）獲得全自動駕駛功能。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190303/59325137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59325137&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv5dwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=b6857042\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59325137&h=b5697db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190303/59325137</a><br />\n<br />\nTes撚+大陸人揸車=馬路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0936e8902cbaf04c842b3312a9288c78850f4ad7","tid":1045336,"uid":190540,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1fd1895ad12319be99a6d4765c0ace6ae5a7c3d","tid":1045336,"uid":44454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"我都抗議股票随意降價"},{"pid":"c6ccf3839f730e07e90ce075415441f34ece7d45","tid":1045336,"uid":52271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:59:50.000Z","msg":"減價都侵犯到佢合法權益<br />\n唔明關法律咩事<br />\n睇黎喺中國，關於法律嘅野都只係一個口號，講乜都要順口加埋落去"},{"pid":"b32637d89f058a449ea5e55eb37b0e36fa691f3c","tid":1045336,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1fd1895ad12319be99a6d4765c0ace6ae5a7c3d","tid":1045336,"uid":44454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"我都抗議股票随意降價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5427f06642c38a652096c7fb24fe3e7b4f6064d","tid":1045336,"uid":35014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c4909ee9f3c711c6b95501da77c1b11cc34c122","tid":1045336,"uid":89530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"Tesla上海建廠　毋須內地合資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180712/20447808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F20447808&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv5dwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=5d4ec313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F20447808&h=a2d9b8e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180712/20447808</a><br />\n<br />\n抵撚死